*****************************************************************
*			User Guideline				*
*****************************************************************
								
This file is released for users who are using SMIC 40nm Logic Salicide 0.9/1.1/1.2/1.8/2.5V low leakage and generic Calibre drc runset. 

1.Option switch setting
There are 3 DRC decks in attached package. 
For main rules(include ESD and Latch-up rules):
SMIC_CalDRC_40GELGLL_0911121825_2TM_V1.12.1_0.drc
SMIC_CalDRC_40GELGLL_0911121825_1TM_V1.12.1_0.drc
For antenna rules:
SMIC_CalDRC_40GELGLL_0911121825_V1.12.1_0.ant


1.1 Option switch setting in main rule
#################################################
